Downplayed Russia and White Supremacists, Whistle-Blower SaysA Homeland Security official accused senior leaders of warping the agency around President Trump’s political interests.The leaders told analysts to downplay the threats of violent white supremacy and of Russian election interference, his whistle-blower complaint said.
Here are five takeaways from Bob Woodward’s new book about President Trump.
